summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5376 for the improvement of 56th Avenue Southwest, from West Andover Street to Hillcrest Avenue on the east; and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues; by constructing watermains, together with fire hydrants and the necessary appurtenances, under Ordinance No. 65384 as amended by Ordinance No. 65503, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
